<!DOCTYPE html>  
<html lang="en">  
<head>  
    <meta charset="UTF-8">  
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">  
    <title>Reward System Tracker</title>  
    <style>  
        * {  
            margin: 0;  
            padding: 0;  
            box-sizing: border-box;  
        }  
          
        body {  
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;  
            padding: 20px;  
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);  
            min-height: 100vh;  
        }  
          
        body.mobile-view {  
            padding: 10px;  
        }  
          
        body.mobile-view .container {  
            padding: 15px;  
        }  
          
        body.mobile-view h1 {  
            font-size: 1.8em;  
        }  
          
        body.mobile-view .balance {  
            font-size: 1.5em;  
            padding: 15px;  
        }  
          
        body.mobile-view .section-title {  
            font-size: 1.3em;  
        }  
          
        body.mobile-view .section {  
            padding: 15px;  
        }  
          
        .container {  
            max-width: 1000px;  
            margin: 0 auto;  
            background: white;  
            padding: 30px;  
            border-radius: 15px;  
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);  
        }  
          
        h1 {  
            text-align: center;  
            color: #667eea;  
            margin-bottom: 30px;  
            font-size: 2.5em;  
            text-transform: uppercase;  
            letter-spacing: 2px;  
        }  
          
        .balance {  
            text-align: center;  
            font-size: 2em;  
            margin-bottom: 40px;  
            padding: 20px;  
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);  
            color: white;  
            border-radius: 10px;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            position: relative;  
        }  
          
        .balance-display {  
            cursor: pointer;  
            transition: transform 0.2s;  
        }  
          
        .balance-display:hover {  
            transform: scale(1.05);  
        }  
          
        .balance-input {  
            font-size: 1em;  
            padding: 10px;  
            width: 150px;  
            border: 3px solid white;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            text-align: center;  
            font-weight: bold;  
        }  
          
        .balance-edit-btn {  
            background: white;  
            color: #667eea;  
            padding: 8px 15px;  
            margin-left: 10px;  
            font-size: 0.5em;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            cursor: pointer;  
            border: none;  
            font-weight: bold;  
        }  
          
        .section {  
            margin-bottom: 35px;  
            padding: 25px;  
            border: 3px solid #667eea;  
            border-radius: 10px;  
            background: #f8f9ff;  
        }  
          
        .section-title {  
            font-size: 1.8em;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            color: #667eea;  
            margin-bottom: 15px;  
            text-transform: uppercase;  
            border-bottom: 3px solid #764ba2;  
            padding-bottom: 10px;  
        }  
          
        .reward-item {  
            margin: 12px 0;  
            padding: 10px;  
            background: white;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            border-left: 4px solid #764ba2;  
        }  
          
        .reward-level {  
            font-weight: bold;  
            color: #333;  
            margin: 5px 0;  
        }  
          
        .checklist {  
            margin-top: 15px;  
        }  
          
        .checkbox-item {  
            display: flex;  
            align-items: center;  
            padding: 10px;  
            margin: 8px 0;  
            background: white;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            border-left: 4px solid #51cf66;  
        }  
          
        .checkbox-item input[type="checkbox"] {  
            width: 20px;  
            height: 20px;  
            margin-right: 15px;  
            cursor: pointer;  
        }  
          
        .checkbox-item label {  
            font-size: 1.1em;  
            cursor: pointer;  
            flex-grow: 1;  
        }  
          
        .checkbox-item input[type="checkbox"]:checked + label {  
            text-decoration: line-through;  
            color: #999;  
        }  
          
        .btn {  
            padding: 12px 25px;  
            font-size: 1em;  
            border: none;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            cursor: pointer;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            transition: transform 0.2s;  
        }  
          
        .btn:hover {  
            transform: scale(1.05);  
        }  
          
        .btn-reset {  
            background: #ffc107;  
            color: white;  
            width: 100%;  
            margin-top: 15px;  
        }  
          
        .btn-add {  
            background: #51cf66;  
            color: white;  
            margin-right: 10px;  
        }  
          
        .btn-delete {  
            background: #ff6b6b;  
            color: white;  
            padding: 8px 15px;  
            font-size: 0.9em;  
        }  
          
        .btn-toggle {  
            background: #667eea;  
            color: white;  
            position: fixed;  
            bottom: 20px;  
            right: 20px;  
            padding: 15px 20px;  
            border-radius: 50px;  
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);  
            z-index: 1000;  
        }  
          
        /* Star Rating Styles */  
        .star-rating-day {  
            background: white;  
            padding: 15px;  
            margin: 10px 0;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating-day-title {  
            font-weight: bold;  
            color: #667eea;  
            margin-bottom: 10px;  
            font-size: 1.1em;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating-group {  
            margin: 10px 0;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating-label {  
            font-size: 0.9em;  
            color: #666;  
            margin-bottom: 5px;  
            display: block;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating {  
            display: inline-flex;  
            flex-direction: row-reverse;  
            gap: 5px;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating input[type="radio"] {  
            display: none;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating label {  
            cursor: pointer;  
            font-size: 30px;  
            color: #ddd;  
            transition: color 0.2s;  
            line-height: 1; /* Ensure stars align vertically */  
        }  
          
        /* Fixed Star for Edge: Use standard unicode star instead of FontAwesome */  
        .star-rating label:before {  
            content: "★";  
            /* Removed font-family dependency to fix Edge issues */  
        }  
          
        .star-rating input[type="radio"]:checked ~ label {  
            color: #FFC107;  
        }  
          
        .star-rating label:hover,  
        .star-rating label:hover ~ label {  
            color: #ffdb70;  
        }  
          
        .rating-average {  
            display: inline-block;  
            margin-left: 20px;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            padding: 5px 15px;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            background: #f0f0f0;  
        }  
          
        .rating-average.high {  
            background: #d3f9d8;  
            color: #2f9e44;  
        }  
          
        .rating-average.low {  
            background: #ffe3e3;  
            color: #c92a2a;  
        }  
          
        /* Piano/Running Tracker Styles */  
        .piano-day {  
            background: white;  
            padding: 10px 15px;  
            margin: 8px 0;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;  
            display: flex;  
            align-items: center;  
            flex-wrap: wrap; /* Fix for mobile */  
            gap: 15px;  
        }  
          
        .piano-day-label {  
            font-weight: bold;  
            color: #667eea;  
            min-width: 100px;  
        }  
          
        .piano-input {  
            padding: 8px;  
            border: 2px solid #667eea;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            width: 100px;  
            font-size: 1em;  
        }  
          
        .piano-unit {  
             white-space: nowrap;  
        }  
          
        .piano-calculator {  
            background: white;  
            padding: 20px;  
            border-radius: 10px;  
            border: 3px solid #51cf66;  
            margin-top: 15px;  
            text-align: center;  
        }  
          
        .piano-total {  
            font-size: 3em;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            color: #51cf66;  
            margin: 20px 0;  
        }  
          
        .updates-section {  
            background: #fff3cd;  
            border-color: #ffc107;  
        }  
          
        .updates-section .section-title {  
            color: #ff6b6b;  
            border-bottom-color: #ffc107;  
        }  
          
        #updatesList {  
            list-style: none;  
        }  
          
        .update-item {  
            background: white;  
            padding: 12px;  
            margin: 10px 0;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;  
            display: flex;  
            justify-content: space-between;  
            align-items: center;  
        }  
          
        .update-input {  
            width: 100%;  
            padding: 12px;  
            font-size: 1em;  
            border: 2px solid #667eea;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            margin-bottom: 10px;  
        }  
          
        .data-sync-buttons {  
            display: flex;  
            gap: 10px;  
            margin-top: 20px;  
            flex-wrap: wrap;  
        }  
          
        .btn-export {  
            background: #51cf66;  
            color: white;  
            flex: 1;  
            min-width: 150px;  
        }  
          
        .btn-import {  
            background: #4dabf7;  
            color: white;  
            flex: 1;  
            min-width: 150px;  
        }  
          
        #importFile {  
            display: none;  
        }  
          
        .modal-overlay {  
            display: none;  
            position: fixed;  
            top: 0;  
            left: 0;  
            width: 100%;  
            height: 100%;  
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);  
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);  
            z-index: 2000;  
            justify-content: center;  
            align-items: center;  
        }  
          
        .modal-overlay.active {  
            display: flex;  
        }  
          
        .modal-content {  
            background: white;  
            padding: 30px;  
            border-radius: 15px;  
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);  
            max-width: 400px;  
            width: 90%;  
            text-align: center;  
        }  
          
        .modal-title {  
            font-size: 1.5em;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            color: #667eea;  
            margin-bottom: 15px;  
        }  
          
        .modal-message {  
            font-size: 1.1em;  
            color: #333;  
            margin-bottom: 25px;  
            line-height: 1.5;  
        }  
          
        .modal-buttons {  
            display: flex;  
            justify-content: flex-end;  
            gap: 10px;  
        }  
          
        .modal-btn {  
            padding: 12px 25px;  
            font-size: 1em;  
            border: none;  
            border-radius: 5px;  
            cursor: pointer;  
            font-weight: bold;  
            transition: transform 0.2s;  
        }  
          
        .modal-btn:hover {  
            transform: scale(1.05);  
        }  
          
        .modal-btn-ok {  
            background: #51cf66;  
            color: white;  
        }  
          
        .modal-btn-error {  
            background: #ff6b6b;  
            color: white;  
        }  

        .projected-earnings {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fff4, #e6ffed);
            border: 2px solid #51cf66;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2f9e44;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .projected-earnings .proj-label {
            color: #555;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .projected-earnings .proj-amount {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            color: #2f9e44;
        }

        .projected-earnings .proj-note {
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: #777;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-left: auto;
        }

        .projected-earnings.zero {
            background: #f8f9ff;
            border-color: #ccc;
            color: #999;
        }

        .projected-earnings.zero .proj-amount {
            color: #999;
        }

        .btn-add-projected {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #51cf66, #2f9e44);
            color: white;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 18px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(81, 207, 102, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-add-projected:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(81, 207, 102, 0.5);
        }

        .total-projected-bar {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .total-projected-bar .total-label {
            font-size: 0.65em;
            opacity: 0.85;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .drive-status-bar {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            font-weight: bold;
            z-index: 999;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        .drive-status-bar.idle    { background: #2f9e44; color: white; }
        .drive-status-bar.saving  { background: #e67700; color: white; }
        .drive-status-bar.error   { background: #c92a2a; color: white; }
        .drive-status-bar.offline { background: #555;    color: #ccc; }
        body { padding-bottom: 40px; }
    </style>  
</head>  
<body>  
    <div class="container">  
        <h1>🎯 System Reward Tracker</h1>  
          
        <div class="balance">  
            <span id="balanceDisplay" class="balance-display" onclick="editBalance()">  
                You Have: $<span id="currentBalance">0</span>  
            </span>  
            <div id="balanceEdit" style="display: none;">  
                You Have: $<input type="number" id="balanceInput" class="balance-input" value="0">  
                <button class="balance-edit-btn" onclick="saveBalance()">Save</button>  
                <button class="balance-edit-btn" onclick="cancelBalanceEdit()">Cancel</button>  
            </div>  
        </div>  
          
        <div class="section">  
            <div class="section-title">💤 SLEEP Before 10</div>  
            <div class="reward-item">  
                <div class="reward-level">5 out of 7 days → $6</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">6 out of 7 days → $8</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">Perfect (7/7) → $10</div>  
            </div>  
              
            <div class="checklist">  
                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 10px;">Weekly Sleep Tracker:</h3>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep1" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep1">Monday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep2" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep2">Tuesday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep3" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep3">Wednesday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep4" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep4">Thursday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep5" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep5">Friday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep6" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep6">Saturday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="sleep7" onchange="saveSleepCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="sleep7">Sunday</label>  
                </div>  
                <button class="btn btn-reset" onclick="resetSleepCheckboxes(); return false;">🔄 Reset Sleep Tracker</button>  
            </div>  
            <div class="projected-earnings zero" id="proj-sleep">
                <span class="proj-label">Earnings:</span>
                <span class="proj-amount" id="proj-sleep-amount">$0</span>
                <span class="proj-note" id="proj-sleep-note">Check more days to earn</span>
            </div>
        </div>  
          
        <div class="section">  
            <div class="section-title">🏃 LEAVE 50 Min Before School / Get Ready 30 Min After</div>  
            <div class="reward-item">  
                <div class="reward-level">5 out of 7 days → $6</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">6 out of 7 days → $8</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">Perfect (7/7) → $10</div>  
            </div>  
              
            <div class="checklist">  
                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 10px;">Weekly On-Time Tracker:</h3>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime1" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime1">Monday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime2" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime2">Tuesday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime3" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime3">Wednesday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime4" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime4">Thursday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime5" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime5">Friday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime6" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime6">Saturday</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="ontime7" onchange="saveOntimeCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="ontime7">Sunday</label>  
                </div>  
                <button class="btn btn-reset" onclick="resetOntimeCheckboxes(); return false;">🔄 Reset On-Time Tracker</button>  
            </div>  
            <div class="projected-earnings zero" id="proj-ontime">
                <span class="proj-label">Earnings:</span>
                <span class="proj-amount" id="proj-ontime-amount">$0</span>
                <span class="proj-note" id="proj-ontime-note">Check more days to earn</span>
            </div>
        </div>  
          
        <div class="section">  
            <div class="section-title">💪 SHOULDER Exercises</div>  
            <div class="reward-item">  
                <div class="reward-level">5 days basic + 3 days IYT + 2 days range of motion</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">(Missing 1 basic OR 1 IYT OR 1 range of motion = normal pay)</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">Normal → $7</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">Perfect → $10</div>  
            </div>  
              
            <div class="checklist">  
                <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 10px;">Weekly Exercise Tracker:</h3>  
                  
                <div style="font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0; color: #764ba2;">Basic Exercises (5 days needed):</div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="basic1" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="basic1">Day 1 - Basic</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="basic2" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="basic2">Day 2 - Basic</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="basic3" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="basic3">Day 3 - Basic</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="basic4" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="basic4">Day 4 - Basic</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="basic5" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="basic5">Day 5 - Basic</label>  
                </div>  
                  
                <div style="font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0; color: #764ba2;">IYT Exercises (3 days needed):</div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="iyt1" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="iyt1">Day 1 - IYT</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="iyt2" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="iyt2">Day 2 - IYT</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="iyt3" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="iyt3">Day 3 - IYT</label>  
                </div>  
                  
                <div style="font-weight: bold; margin: 15px 0; color: #764ba2;">Range of Motion (2 days needed):</div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="rom1" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="rom1">Day 1 - Range of Motion</label>  
                </div>  
                <div class="checkbox-item">  
                    <input type="checkbox" id="rom2" onchange="saveCheckboxes(); updateProjectedEarnings();">  
                    <label for="rom2">Day 2 - Range of Motion</label>  
                </div>  
                  
                <button class="btn btn-reset" onclick="resetCheckboxes(); return false;">🔄 Reset Exercise Tracker</button>  
            </div>  
            <div class="projected-earnings zero" id="proj-shoulder">
                <span class="proj-label">Earnings:</span>
                <span class="proj-amount" id="proj-shoulder-amount">$0</span>
                <span class="proj-note" id="proj-shoulder-note">Complete exercises to earn</span>
            </div>
        </div>  
          
        <div class="section">  
            <div class="section-title">🎹 PIANO Playing Goals</div>  
            <div class="reward-item">  
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-style: italic; color: #666;">  
                    Note: Schene lesson counts as 2 hours, other lessons don't count  
                </div>  
                <div class="reward-level">10 hours → $13</div>  
                <div class="reward-level">11 hours → $15</div>  
